text: LA-17 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Chaudhary Muhammad Yasin Gulshan of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Abbaspur in Poonch District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
